{
  "stem": "9995.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They started in our city-- in some other places maybe sooner-- in our city, it started in June, 1942.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the first very massive deportation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother's [SIGHS] two sisters and grandfather went.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one sister still stayed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now my aunt's husband, as they were going, they ask him to run.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he couldn't run too fast, because he was carrying a lot of clothes, everything on his back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so they shot him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the end, who didn't know who else went, said to one man from these ordinances, the Jewish police, said, tell-- tell my family that-- because she knew that he knew us-- that I am a widow.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she-- she went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the streets were flowing with blood because a lot of people were killed as they were being taken.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was absolutely dreadful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we still believed that the-- they-- some of them who were not killed on the streets, that they will survive.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we didn't know that they went to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some may be in Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, at any rate, they were killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you see, they said in ghetto before that you should have some employment which is recognized.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, my mother was working in a factory called Optima, in the office.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, since you know how to sew, I suggest that you go over there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And since I learned in school also how to embroider, I was making the buttonholes on the uniforms.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I had a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I got so called [NON-ENGLISH], with a stamp that I could stay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, my mother's sister believed that, oh, maybe it's just a hoax, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's why they-- they-- whoever didn't have this thing went.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Later on, they were taking just anybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
